{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I still remember the day in school"},{"time":3000,"text":"when our teacher told us"},{"time":6000,"text":"that the world population had become"},{"time":8000,"text":"three billion people,"},{"time":10000,"text":"and that was in 1960."},{"time":14000,"text":"I'm going to talk now about"},{"time":16000,"text":"how world population has changed from that year"},{"time":18000,"text":"and into the future,"},{"time":20000,"text":"but I will not use digital technology,"},{"time":23000,"text":"as I've done during my first five TEDTalks."},{"time":26000,"text":"Instead, I have progressed,"},{"time":29000,"text":"and I am, today, launching"},{"time":31000,"text":"a brand new analog teaching technology"},{"time":34000,"text":"that I picked up from IKEA:"},{"time":36000,"text":"this box."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38000,"text":"This box contains one billion people."},{"time":40000,"text":"And our teacher told us"},{"time":42000,"text":"that the industrialized world, 1960,"},{"time":45000,"text":"had one billion people."},{"time":47000,"text":"In the developing world, she said,"},{"time":49000,"text":"they had two billion people."},{"time":51000,"text":"And they lived away then."},{"time":53000,"text":"There was a big gap between"},{"time":55000,"text":"the one billion in the industrialized world"},{"time":57000,"text":"and the two billion in the developing world."},{"time":60000,"text":"In the industrialized world,"},{"time":62000,"text":"people were healthy,"},{"time":64000,"text":"educated, rich,"},{"time":66000,"text":"and they had small families."},{"time":68000,"text":"And their aspiration"},{"time":70000,"text":"was to buy a car."},{"time":72000,"text":"And in 1960, all Swedes were saving"},{"time":75000,"text":"to try to buy a Volvo like this."},{"time":78000,"text":"This was the economic level at which Sweden was."},{"time":81000,"text":"But in contrast to this,"},{"time":83000,"text":"in the developing world, far away,"},{"time":85000,"text":"the aspiration of the average family there"},{"time":88000,"text":"was to have food for the day."},{"time":91000,"text":"They were saving"},{"time":93000,"text":"to be able to buy a pair of shoes."},{"time":96000,"text":"There was an enormous gap in the world"},{"time":98000,"text":"when I grew up."},{"time":100000,"text":"And this gap between the West and the rest"},{"time":103000,"text":"has created a mindset of the world,"},{"time":106000,"text":"which we still use linguistically"},{"time":108000,"text":"when we talk about \"the West\""},{"time":110000,"text":"and \"the Developing World.\""},{"time":112000,"text":"But the world has changed,"},{"time":114000,"text":"and it's overdue to upgrade that mindset"},{"time":117000,"text":"and that taxonomy of the world, and to understand it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120000,"text":"And that's what I'm going to show you,"},{"time":122000,"text":"because since 1960"},{"time":125000,"text":"what has happened in the world up to 2010"},{"time":128000,"text":"is that a staggering"},{"time":130000,"text":"four billion people"},{"time":132000,"text":"have been added to the world population."},{"time":134000,"text":"Just look how many."},{"time":136000,"text":"The world population has doubled"},{"time":138000,"text":"since I went to school."},{"time":142000,"text":"And of course, there's been economic growth in the West."},{"time":145000,"text":"A lot of companies have happened to grow the economy,"},{"time":148000,"text":"so the Western population moved over to here."},{"time":151000,"text":"And now their aspiration is not only to have a car."},{"time":154000,"text":"Now they want to have a holiday on a very remote destination"},{"time":157000,"text":"and they want to fly."},{"time":159000,"text":"So this is where they are today."},{"time":161000,"text":"And the most successful of the developing countries,"},{"time":164000,"text":"they have moved on, you know,"},{"time":166000,"text":"and they have become emerging economies, we call them."},{"time":169000,"text":"They are now buying cars."},{"time":171000,"text":"And what happened a month ago"},{"time":173000,"text":"was that the Chinese company, Geely,"},{"time":175000,"text":"they acquired the Volvo company,"},{"time":178000,"text":"and then finally the Swedes understood that"},{"time":180000,"text":"something big had happened in the world."},{"time":182000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":185000,"text":"So there they are."},{"time":187000,"text":"And the tragedy is that the two billion over here"},{"time":190000,"text":"that is struggling for food and shoes,"},{"time":193000,"text":"they are still almost as poor"},{"time":195000,"text":"as they were 50 years ago."},{"time":197000,"text":"The new thing is that"},{"time":199000,"text":"we have the biggest pile of billions, the three billions here,"},{"time":202000,"text":"which are also becoming emerging economies,"},{"time":205000,"text":"because they are quite healthy, relatively well-educated,"},{"time":208000,"text":"and they already also have two to three children"},{"time":210000,"text":"per woman, as those [richer also] have."},{"time":213000,"text":"And their aspiration now"},{"time":215000,"text":"is, of course, to buy a bicycle,"},{"time":218000,"text":"and then later on they would like to have a motorbike also."},{"time":221000,"text":"But this is the world"},{"time":224000,"text":"we have today,"},{"time":226000,"text":"no longer any gap."},{"time":228000,"text":"But the distance from the poorest here, the very poorest,"},{"time":231000,"text":"to the very richest over here is wider than ever."},{"time":234000,"text":"But there is a continuous world"},{"time":236000,"text":"from walking, biking,"},{"time":238000,"text":"driving, flying --"},{"time":240000,"text":"there are people on all levels,"},{"time":242000,"text":"and most people tend to be somewhere in the middle."},{"time":246000,"text":"This is the new world we have today"},{"time":248000,"text":"in 2010."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251000,"text":"And what will happen in the future?"},{"time":255000,"text":"Well, I'm going to project"},{"time":257000,"text":"into 2050."},{"time":259000,"text":"I was in Shanghai recently,"},{"time":262000,"text":"and I listened to what's happening in China,"},{"time":264000,"text":"and it's pretty sure that they will catch up,"},{"time":267000,"text":"just as Japan did."},{"time":269000,"text":"All the projections [say that] this one [billion] will [only] grow with"},{"time":271000,"text":"one to two or three percent."},{"time":273000,"text":"[But this second] grows with seven, eight percent, and then they will end up here."},{"time":276000,"text":"They will start flying."},{"time":278000,"text":"And these"},{"time":280000,"text":"lower or middle income countries, the emerging income countries,"},{"time":283000,"text":"they will also forge forwards economically."},{"time":286000,"text":"And if,"},{"time":288000,"text":"but only if,"},{"time":290000,"text":"we invest in the right green technology --"},{"time":293000,"text":"so that we can avoid severe climate change,"},{"time":295000,"text":"and energy can still be relatively cheap --"},{"time":298000,"text":"then they will move all the way up here."},{"time":301000,"text":"And they will start to buy"},{"time":303000,"text":"electric cars."},{"time":305000,"text":"This is what we will find there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308000,"text":"So what about the poorest two billion?"},{"time":310000,"text":"What about the poorest two billion here?"},{"time":313000,"text":"Will they move on?"},{"time":315000,"text":"Well, here population [growth] comes in"},{"time":317000,"text":"because there [among emerging economies] we already have two to three children per woman,"},{"time":320000,"text":"family planning is widely used,"},{"time":322000,"text":"and population growth is coming to an end."},{"time":324000,"text":"Here [among the poorest], population is growing."},{"time":327000,"text":"So these [poorest] two billion will, in the next decades,"},{"time":330000,"text":"increase to three billion,"},{"time":332000,"text":"and they will thereafter"},{"time":334000,"text":"increase to four billion."},{"time":336000,"text":"There is nothing --"},{"time":338000,"text":"but a nuclear war of a kind we've never seen --"},{"time":341000,"text":"that can stop this [growth] from happening."},{"time":344000,"text":"Because we already have this [growth] in process."},{"time":347000,"text":"But if, and only if,"},{"time":349000,"text":"[the poorest] get out of poverty,"},{"time":351000,"text":"they get education, they get improved child survival,"},{"time":353000,"text":"they can buy a bicycle and a cell phone and come [to live] here,"},{"time":356000,"text":"then population growth"},{"time":358000,"text":"will stop in 2050."},{"time":361000,"text":"We cannot have people on this level"},{"time":363000,"text":"looking for food and shoes"},{"time":365000,"text":"because then we get continued population growth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":368000,"text":"And let me show you why"},{"time":370000,"text":"by converting back to the old-time"},{"time":373000,"text":"digital technology."},{"time":375000,"text":"Here I have on the screen"},{"time":377000,"text":"my country bubbles."},{"time":379000,"text":"Every bubble is a country. The size is population."},{"time":381000,"text":"The colors show the continent."},{"time":383000,"text":"The yellow on there is the Americas;"},{"time":385000,"text":"dark blue is Africa; brown is Europe;"},{"time":387000,"text":"green is the Middle East"},{"time":390000,"text":"and this light blue is South Asia."},{"time":392000,"text":"That's India and this is China. Size is population."},{"time":394000,"text":"Here I have children per woman:"},{"time":397000,"text":"two children, four children, six children, eight children --"},{"time":399000,"text":"big families, small families."},{"time":402000,"text":"The year is 1960."},{"time":404000,"text":"And down here, child survival,"},{"time":406000,"text":"the percentage of children surviving childhood"},{"time":408000,"text":"up to starting school:"},{"time":410000,"text":"60 percent, 70 percent, 80 percent, 90,"},{"time":413000,"text":"and almost 100 percent, as we have today"},{"time":415000,"text":"in the wealthiest and healthiest countries."},{"time":417000,"text":"But look, this is the world my teacher talked about in 1960:"},{"time":420000,"text":"one billion Western world here --"},{"time":423000,"text":"high child-survival, small families --"},{"time":426000,"text":"and all the rest,"},{"time":428000,"text":"the rainbow of developing countries,"},{"time":430000,"text":"with very large families"},{"time":432000,"text":"and poor child survival."}]},{"cues":[{"time":434000,"text":"What has happened? I start the world. Here we go."},{"time":437000,"text":"Can you see, as the years pass by, child survival is increasing?"},{"time":440000,"text":"They get soap, hygiene, education,"},{"time":442000,"text":"vaccination, penicillin"},{"time":444000,"text":"and then family planning. Family size is decreasing."},{"time":447000,"text":"[When] they get up to 90-percent child survival, then families decrease,"},{"time":450000,"text":"and most of the Arab countries in the Middle East"},{"time":452000,"text":"is falling down there [to small families]."},{"time":454000,"text":"Look, Bangladesh catching up with India."},{"time":456000,"text":"The whole emerging world"},{"time":459000,"text":"joins the Western world"},{"time":461000,"text":"with good child survival"},{"time":463000,"text":"and small family size,"},{"time":465000,"text":"but we still have the poorest billion."},{"time":467000,"text":"Can you see the poorest billion,"},{"time":469000,"text":"those [two] boxes I had over here?"},{"time":472000,"text":"They are still up here."},{"time":474000,"text":"And they still have a child survival"},{"time":476000,"text":"of only 70 to 80 percent,"},{"time":478000,"text":"meaning that if you have six children born,"},{"time":480000,"text":"there will be at least four who survive"},{"time":482000,"text":"to the next generation."},{"time":484000,"text":"And the population will double in one generation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"So the only way"},{"time":489000,"text":"of really getting world population [growth] to stop"},{"time":492000,"text":"is to continue to improve child survival"},{"time":494000,"text":"to 90 percent."},{"time":496000,"text":"That's why investments by Gates Foundation,"},{"time":498000,"text":"UNICEF and aid organizations,"},{"time":500000,"text":"together with national government in the poorest countries,"},{"time":502000,"text":"are so good;"},{"time":504000,"text":"because they are actually"},{"time":506000,"text":"helping us to reach"},{"time":508000,"text":"a sustainable population size of the world."},{"time":510000,"text":"We can stop at nine billion if we do the right things."},{"time":513000,"text":"Child survival is the new green."},{"time":516000,"text":"It's only by child survival"},{"time":518000,"text":"that we will stop population growth."},{"time":521000,"text":"And will it happen?"},{"time":523000,"text":"Well, I'm not an optimist,"},{"time":526000,"text":"neither am I a pessimist."},{"time":528000,"text":"I'm a very serious \"possibilist.\""},{"time":531000,"text":"It's a new category where we take emotion apart,"},{"time":534000,"text":"and we just work analytically with the world."},{"time":536000,"text":"It can be done."},{"time":539000,"text":"We can have a much more just world."},{"time":542000,"text":"With green technology"},{"time":544000,"text":"and with investments to alleviate poverty,"},{"time":546000,"text":"and global governance,"},{"time":548000,"text":"the world can become like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550000,"text":"And look at the position of the old West."},{"time":553000,"text":"Remember when this blue box was all alone,"},{"time":556000,"text":"leading the world, living its own life."},{"time":559000,"text":"This will not happen [again]."},{"time":561000,"text":"The role of the old West in the new world"},{"time":564000,"text":"is to become the foundation"},{"time":566000,"text":"of the modern world --"},{"time":568000,"text":"nothing more, nothing less."},{"time":570000,"text":"But it's a very important role."},{"time":572000,"text":"Do it well and get used to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":574000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}